{"tid":2015638,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【上月宣布退出樂壇】關淑怡稱法治已死　鬧爆李慧琼：一堆渣滓","createTime":"2020-05-13T23:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T00:42:28.000Z","uid":35519,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2da7a73e94e4eeec611282f51883febf96194c1","tid":2015638,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【上月宣布退出樂壇】<br />\n關淑怡稱法治已死 <br />\n鬧爆李慧琼：一堆渣滓</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200513/1536pix/1589361782_df96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200513%2F1536pix%2F1589361782_df96.png&h=92f351ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200513/1536pix/1589361547_7388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200513%2F1536pix%2F1589361547_7388.jpg&h=cca23a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前立法會鬧出泛民與建制派爭奪內會主席，當中民建聯主席李慧琼，在未經選舉產生下，自封「主席」並將多名泛民議員驅逐離場，期間人民力量陳志全更被工聯會郭偉強粗暴對待，拖扯對方離場。<br />\n<br />\n53歲的關淑怡Shirley，日前在IG發文，大鬧日前強行爭奪內會主席的李慧琼，指「她與她的波士，正將香港毀滅」，並指「期待第三之世界大戰，金錢與權力會殺死他們」，更大鬧建制派是「嘔心，一堆渣滓」！<br />\n<br />\n去年反修例風波期間，Shirley與黃耀明合唱《快樂到死》，遭內地網民指黃耀明是「封殺名單」，導致關淑怡所有歌曲在內地Apple Music下架，但Shirley依然力撐黃耀明，除了發文鬧部分內地網民「沒人權又沒普及教育的一群」，更指&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n繼續閱讀，請訂閱《壹週刊》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_740235_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_740235_0&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHCuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=4bd4eedc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_740235_0&h=1cf14af9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_740235_0</a>"},{"pid":"b8756a5b7a80fc748d31d9b54e7a0fc69203271c","tid":2015638,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\